trans-unit.source: Specifies drill-down and node viewing mode for an <xref:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner>, such as Flowcharts, that are used to compose activities.
trans-unit.target: Angir neddrilling og noden visningsmodus for en <xref:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner>, for eksempel flytskjemaer, som brukes til å opprette aktiviteter.</xref:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Drilling down into the UI elements is allowed by default.
trans-unit.target: Drille ned i UI-elementer er tillatt som standard.

trans-unit.source: It can be disallowed by setting the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A> property to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Det kan ikke ved å angi den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A>egenskapen `false`.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A>

trans-unit.source: Child nodes are not always collapsed by default, but can be set to always collapse by setting the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Underordnede noder skjules ikke alltid som standard, men kan settes til Skjul alltid ved å angi den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute*> class.

The default values assigned by this constructor are `true` for the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A> property and `false` for the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdiene tilordnet av denne konstruktøren `true` for den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A>egenskapen og `false` for den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AlwaysCollapseChildren%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesignerOptionsAttribute.AllowDrillIn%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether drilling down one level into an <xref:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner> is allowed.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om drille ned eller opp ett nivå i en <xref:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner>er tillatt.</xref:system.Activities.Presentation.ActivityDesigner>
